{"tid":1066593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"決定勇敢承擔責任   賴清德領表登記民進黨台灣總統初選","createTime":"2019-03-18T03:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T23:00:54.000Z","uid":35790,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"218b2f24760c03a1d71088637c79f255d3310bcc","tid":1066593,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T03:56:36.000Z","msg":"決定勇敢承擔責任 賴清德領表登記民進黨總統初選<br />\n<br />\n2019-03-18 <br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕民進黨今天展開總統大選黨內初選登記，據了解，前行政院長賴清德決定勇敢承擔責任，並向媒體透露，今天上午11點半在長老教會長老、長榮中學校長王昭卿陪同下，前往黨中央領表登記。<br />\n<br />\n民進黨本週啟動總統初選作業，今（18日）起至週五（22日）開放領表、登記。賴清德昨被問下一步動向時回應，在立委輔選過程中傾聽到基層民眾聲音，會進一步思考，今天隨即就傳出將勇於承擔，領表登記投入黨內初選。<br />\n<br />\n至於已表態競選連任的蔡英文總統預計本週完成登記後，將在21日啟程出訪南太友邦拚外交。<br />\n<br />\n兩組以上參加初選 4/10進行初選民調<br />\n<br />\n民進黨規劃，總統初選22日截止登記後，4月4日至9日間舉辦政見發表會；若有兩組人馬以上參加初選，4月10日即進行初選民調；4月17日中執會公告總統初選候選人提名名單。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"283add374c8e1b23b27ff453b953badd7ee2f4f2","tid":1066593,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T03:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1098df144139c054c392ae669ad659d09083fb","tid":1066593,"uid":205275,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:39:26.000Z","msg":"支持賴神屌打小英<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3909fb8383b29ce9c28d04f58aa0de6088176ab","tid":1066593,"uid":155095,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ab1098df144139c054c392ae669ad659d09083fb","tid":1066593,"uid":205275,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:39:26.000Z","msg":"支持賴神屌打小英<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"自相殘殺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfd8dbf6b8645c0e3f4947b7e0b83450472bca5","tid":1066593,"uid":179908,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:59:44.000Z","msg":"民進黨就算english要競逐連任都有初選<br />\n國民黨如果仲夠膽徵召一定有人唔復<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4012dceb2441f874c5c32da07a38c0902dc228f9","tid":1066593,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:20:12.000Z","msg":"英姐會唔會成為第一個連任唔到既台灣總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3750190660c64c34b7b54b1252d452c323dfeb0c","tid":1066593,"uid":157330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:20:23.000Z","msg":"賴清德民調贏硬蔡英文"},{"pid":"9314a1e54c33350859400b766f7624728024b315","tid":1066593,"uid":205275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3909fb8383b29ce9c28d04f58aa0de6088176ab","tid":1066593,"uid":155095,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ab1098df144139c054c392ae669ad659d09083fb","tid":1066593,"uid":205275,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:39:26.000Z","msg":"支持賴神屌打小英<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"自相殘殺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:25:56.000Z","msg":"呢D叫君子之爭呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f651c2917f97f7cee729356a6fa79bbea50bc106","tid":1066593,"uid":77813,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:09:32.000Z","msg":"據三立新聞網報道，賴清德讚揚國民黨籍高雄市長韓國瑜，指他是「百年難得一見的政治奇才」，並直言期待和韓在2020年進行一場君子之爭，「贏的人帶領台灣往前走」<br />\n<br />\n串佢定咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fd89c52054fe3274c401bc6f7dfe7cd0f017f8","tid":1066593,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:39:42.000Z","msg":"賴主張訂立新憲法 維護台灣主權"},{"pid":"6c1a974ba4e7a2760df8e864d5f13977bb7f8791","tid":1066593,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:44:03.000Z","msg":"國民黨係咪派王金平，呢條友好似細細個就聽佢霸左立法院長做左好耐"},{"pid":"95ef956ea04b76d6aca5de7d522c280bd0d6353c","tid":1066593,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:48:29.000Z","msg":"三腳督對決 綠民調：賴清德出馬勝朱韓 柯文哲排第三<br />\n<br />\n2019年03月18日 12:25 工商 崔慈悌<br />\n賴清德宣布參與2020總統黨內初選，新台灣國策智庫今天公布最新民調，如果柯文哲不出馬，國民黨以朱立倫和韓國瑜最強，賴PK朱，賴以46.6％比44.1％勝出，賴PK韓也以48.6％比44.6％獲勝，即使「三腳督」，國民黨無論是派韓還是朱，賴支持度都居冠，柯P則排第三。<br />\n<br />\n新台灣國策智庫今天公布「2020總統大選投票意向」最新民調，如果柯文哲不出馬參選2020，民進黨派出賴清德，在國民黨派出吳敦義情況下，賴清德以64.8％支持度大勝吳敦義的22.7％。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果國民黨派出朱立倫，賴清德可獲46.6％的支持度，仍舊勝過朱立倫的44.1％；即使國 民黨派出「最強候選人」韓國瑜出馬，賴也以48.6％的支持度，勝過韓國瑜的44.6％；國民黨若派出王金平，賴以49.6％贏過王金平的36.7％。<br />\n<br />\n如果柯文哲決定出馬參選，在三腳督情況下，國民黨派朱立倫出馬，支持度的排名為賴35.1％、朱31.8％、柯27.9％，賴清德仍可勝出，柯則排第三。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">國民黨若派韓國瑜出馬，支持度的排名為賴35.3％、韓34.7％、柯24.1％，賴清德仍可勝出，柯也是排第三。</span>新台灣國策智庫執行長陳致中表示，從民調來看，韓國瑜並沒有想像的這麼強。<br />\n<br />\n不過他指出，賴所以能下定決心投入參選，與這次台南選情狀況有關，如果民進黨在該選區「很好選」，賴不一定會出馬，賴應是看到民進黨的困境和艱難，希望透過自己投入參選，要讓民進黨明年總統選舉也能夠像台南選情一樣，在艱難的過程中，到最後也能取得勝選。<br />\n(工商 )<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190318001782-260407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20190318001782-260407&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4MyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=ae09ce9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190318001782-260407</a>"},{"pid":"2a2bc53dc1a15ed79711163766e113bcb6dd8836","tid":1066593,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4012dceb2441f874c5c32da07a38c0902dc228f9","tid":1066593,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:20:12.000Z","msg":"英姐會唔會成為第一個連任唔到既台灣總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:52:47.000Z","msg":"李登輝都冇連任"},{"pid":"c701d766c546457d8b7959c6931d9b09b7757707","tid":1066593,"uid":109780,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:12:03.000Z","msg":"韩国瑜一统中国，取代习近平"},{"pid":"069b6d3925fb9b26ff074eaa6a3b50956b60614e","tid":1066593,"uid":147317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:20:05.000Z","msg":"立委補選話俾綠知，統獨係救番總統同立委大選既唯一方法。 係麻唔會得番3分1立委<br />\n獨派先逼賴清德黎要參加<br />\n<br />\nkmt依家應該會逼韓參加，朱立倫應該無咩勝率"},{"pid":"d94beea8e6f391168602388cd66348487d657644","tid":1066593,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a2bc53dc1a15ed79711163766e113bcb6dd8836","tid":1066593,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4012dceb2441f874c5c32da07a38c0902dc228f9","tid":1066593,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:20:12.000Z","msg":"英姐會唔會成為第一個連任唔到既台灣總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:52:47.000Z","msg":"李登輝都冇連任"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:20:09.000Z","msg":"1988年1月13日，時任國民黨主席及中華民國總統的蔣經國逝世，李登輝以副總統身份繼任總統。"},{"pid":"9f0b370a54b179642ea208a940f4f216f1fb50a2","tid":1066593,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a2bc53dc1a15ed79711163766e113bcb6dd8836","tid":1066593,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4012dceb2441f874c5c32da07a38c0902dc228f9","tid":1066593,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:20:12.000Z","msg":"英姐會唔會成為第一個連任唔到既台灣總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:52:47.000Z","msg":"李登輝都冇連任"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:22:59.000Z","msg":"點會無，做左唔止10年<br />\n不過你要計，老蔣同佢個仔中間好似有一個，唔記得叫咩名"},{"pid":"3f265dd4df9053ee565360e10ff16c21cf282eba","tid":1066593,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f0b370a54b179642ea20